significantly impaired over recent years, as natural land cover has been
urbanized or converted,to agricultural uses. We first generated new maps
of land cover and major land uses from satellite and airborne imagery
for the watershed. The SWAT model Output was checked against six
streamflow gauges in the watershed. At the monthly time step, we found
that the precalibrated model performed well at all gauges, with the
