returns per hectare at 4{\%} for options A-E were {\$}11.67, {\$}-3.97,
{\$}32.43, {\$}22.29, and {\$}23.35, respectively, and at 8{\%}, {\$}-17.35,
{\$}-25.74, {\$}8.58, {\$}3.02, and {\$}17.98, respectively.},
author = {GORENZEL, W P and MASTRUP, S A and FITZHUGH, E L},
